## MANDATORY License Requirements
- **Premium License Required** for all Training Lab features
- License validation on every endpoint
- Feature limitation based on license tier
- Usage tracking and limits enforcement

## MANDATORY Security Requirements
- All endpoints require JWT authentication
- Workspace ownership validation
- Rate limiting: 30 requests per minute per user
- Input sanitization and validation
- Secure LLM API key handling

## MANDATORY Performance Requirements
- Response time < 2 seconds for list operations
- Response time < 5 seconds for creation operations
- Response time < 10 seconds for test operations
- Pagination for all list endpoints
- Efficient database queries with proper indexing

